  rounds:
  - victimMessage: "Anh Mathew n\xF3i g\u1EEDi qu\xE0 cho ch\u1ECB r\u1ED3i, ki\u1EC7n
      h\xE0ng m\xE3 s\u1ED1 bao nhi\xEAu em?"
    scriptToType: Da kien hang tu my cua chi dang bi giu o hai quan.
    timeLimit: 15
    hasDistraction: 0
    distractionMessage: 
  - victimMessage: "Tr\u1EDDi \u01A1i, trong \u0111\xF3 c\xF3 \u0111\xF4 la v\u1EDBi
      trang s\u1EE9c \u0111\xF3, l\xE0m sao l\u1EA5y ra?"
    scriptToType: Chi phai dong phi thue thu nhap de lanh hang ra.
    timeLimit: 15
    hasDistraction: 1
    distractionMessage: "B\xE0 n\xE0y m\xEA trai T\xE2y l\u1EAFm, b\xE0o m\u1EA1nh
      v\xE0o!"
  - victimMessage: "Bao nhi\xEAu v\u1EADy em, ch\u1ECB lo qu\xE1."
    scriptToType: Da phi la 10 trieu, chi chuyen ngay keo bi tich thu.
    timeLimit: 15
    hasDistraction: 0
    distractionMessage: 
  - victimMessage: "Ch\u1ECB kh\xF4ng c\xF3 \u0111\u1EE7, em linh \u0111\u1ED9ng
      cho ch\u1ECB \u0111\xF3ng tr\u01B0\u1EDBc 5 tri\u1EC7u \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
      ko?"
    scriptToType: Vay chi chuyen tam truoc roi em linh dong cho.
    timeLimit: 15
    hasDistraction: 1
    distractionMessage: "\u0110\u1EEBng c\xF3 k\xEC k\xE8o! V\xE9t s\u1EA1ch t\xFAi
      b\u1EA3 cho tao!"
  - victimMessage: "Ch\u1ECB chuy\u1EC3n r\u1ED3i \u0111\xF3, ch\u1EEBng n\xE0o ch\u1ECB
      nh\u1EADn \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c qu\xE0 v\u1EADy em?"
    scriptToType: Da trong chieu nay xe chuyen hang se qua nha chi.
    timeLimit: 15
    hasDistraction: 0
    distractionMessage: 
